## <a id="reqs"></a>Requirements

Wavefront by VMware Nozzle for PCF has the following requirements:

+ Read-only administrative access to the Doppler Firehose and Cloud Controller.
+ A Wavefront account and API token.
+ A PCF Quota with a route and a port available.
+ A PCF TCP domain and port for the Wavefront Proxy.

